title: Strong transboundary electron transfer of high-entropy quantum-dots driving rapid hydrogen evolution kinetics
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, Advance Article
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE01825G, Paper
Hao Zhao, Mengyuan Liu, Qiansen Wang, YuZe Li, Yubin Chen, Yanping Zhu, Zhouying Yue, Jun Li, Guoliang Wang, Zhiqing Zou, Qingqing Cheng, Hui Yang
Strong transboundary electron transfer in high-entropy quantum-dots significantly accelerates the Tafel kinetics in HER, which effectively reduces the cost of cathode catalyst in proton exchange membrane water electrolysis (PEMWE).
